ActAn Act to enact the Impact Assessment Act and the Canadian Energy Regulator Act, to amend the Navigation Protection Act and to make consequential amendments to other Acts
SubjectOrder Fixing August 29, 2019 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of that Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing August 29, 2019 as the day on which section 60 and subsection 61(5) of AN ACT TO ENACT THE IMPACT ASSESSMENT ACT AND THE CANADIAN ENERGY REGULATOR ACT, TO AMEND THE NAVIGATION PROTECTION ACT AND TO MAKE CONSEQUENTIAL AMENDMENTS TO OTHER ACTS, chapter 28 of the Statutes of Canada, 2019, COME INTO FORCE.
